==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cuckooflower
<hw>Cuck"oo*flow`er</hw> <pr>(-flou`?r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A species of <gen>Cardamine</gen> (<spn>Cardamine
pratensis</spn>), or lady's smock. Its leaves are used in salads. Also,
the ragged robin (<spn>Lychnis Flos-cuculi</spn>).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

